    "en": {
      "title": "A Pop Group",
      "content": "This is the pop group 4 x 4 (Four by Four). Melanie Ryan is from Australia. Yves Lacoste is from France. Cath and George Walters are from England. They're on tour in the United States.\n'We're in New York. We're at the Radio City Music Hall. It's great!'\nWho is married in 4x4? Yves: 'I'm not married.' George and Cath: 'We aren't married!' Melanie: 'I am!'",
